mylist.usage:
`%1$smylist query [track number]`: Show your list entries
`%1$smylist set <track number> <keyword/link>`: Add or update your list
`%1$smylist play <track number>`: Play specific track
`%1$smylist remove <track number>`: Remove track in your list
